name: Dig Up!
description:
You are an underground explorer who got stuck in the deeps with his drilling machine. You have to get to the surface! When you run out of fuel, you sink all the way back down - but you get a chance to upgrade your machine before your next try. Good luck!

Arrow keys or W A D keys to accelerate and steer, space bar for a short boost of speed (when you have charges). Avoid rocks, collect other pickups! And always Dig up!

Music: Peenzee O'Traak by Eugenio Mininni (from Mixkit)
